    "body": "Don't use `remote` for ipc. There are actually 2 different ipc modules in atom-shell. `require('ipc')` uses the right one in respect to where you're calling it from.\nHave a look at\nhttps://github.com/atom/atom-shell/blob/master/docs/api/ipc-browser.md\nand\nhttps://github.com/atom/atom-shell/blob/master/docs/api/ipc-renderer.md\n"
